Package: rcitoid
Type: Package
Title: Client for 'Citoid'
Description: Client for 'Citoid' (<https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Citoid>),
    an API for getting citations for various scholarly work identifiers
    found on 'Wikipedia'.
